Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点儿啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件…连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和芽间穿的那件很像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么穿成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看清楚啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这次错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来像芽间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看见芽间吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 看上去像芽间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底像不像!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 芽间会死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会是你的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:02:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说是我的错了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没对芽间说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间就不会死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害死芽间的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间要是出现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该出现在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变鬼也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该在我的面前!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 芽间已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也…不在这个世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间说「我就在这里」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在说那种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…芽间让我对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 「发夹 谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不太清楚 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样放他走好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是一早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…知道了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…多少有些怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从很早开始 我就陪他一起放学回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作要给神秘女朋友送礼物的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女装的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色 带丝带的连衣裙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脓要放出来才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经烂到芯里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把脓全部放出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就剩不下什么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「发夹 谢谢 对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等等啊 仁碳要走掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉就走掉吧 那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间才不是什么丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这个很适合 芽间你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合 我最喜欢的芽间!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁碳走掉了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间必须去追仁碳 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着眼镜好像差点儿呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…看不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…间…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃点儿什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我想想…阿健拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了最近都没看到那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.45,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}注：阿健拉面已停产
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 那怎么办呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不用特意跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里有的东西就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在雪集那里 而是在我这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵也好 妄想也好 怎么都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实只是不去想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起 很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仁碳在一起 很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 即使不认真去想也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我总这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太受欢迎啦 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有阿健拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就买了别的代替
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替…这么多?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快点儿坐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话要说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喀嚓喀嚓」冰棍要 要化了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮我 实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你在说些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正按自己的做法来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…各种做法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不像雪集那么执着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有自己的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也 有很多自己的事情要忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没闲工夫一直关心你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 今天也好累…哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是怎么回事 要开party么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 「喀嚓喀嚓」好可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃吗 …啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「自己的事情」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么好忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭 上网 睡觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏 睡觉 吃饭 …
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在不断重复吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.02,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(623,607)}第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(781,684)}隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时候就直接坐电车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他大概7点下班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 鸣子最后能来太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经算上鸣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发短信拒绝我的时候我都不知道怎么办好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会惹凉君生气的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和凉没关系!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子最近都不大和我们来往了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还商量过要不要和你绝交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的春菜 玩笑过火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we talk about intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we do not mean the ability to get a good score
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on a certain kind of test
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or even the ability to do well in school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,these are at best only…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下一班要等30分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时一样呢 你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过平常了 反倒叫人难受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是希望我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我骂你「女装男」么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许那样我会更感激你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便拿我寻求心理上的平衡好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多时候悬崖勒马了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…然后就在短信里写了「喜欢～」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实生活太充实了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门坐电车 跑到城里来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还拿着那么大的购物袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠衣服之类的来改变一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会受不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多意义上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱的好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害好厉害好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一首 小凉选歌～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快选歌啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要发出那么淫荡的声音啦 JK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.82,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}注：选歌那个动词也有插入的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉 哪首都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.02,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}哈哈 哪首好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.06,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}春菜 冷静点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得高兴么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你好像在勉强自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有勉强啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 咱们两个偷溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和鸣子要退出咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 等 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子好像身体不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也要早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要看ONE PIECE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE是后天播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣子 之后要好好给我们讲讲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站是 这边?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是一起到车站 这 这样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷溜可不是那个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我 真的是喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想稍微休息一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…我是真的身体不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 休息一下不就好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 ONE PIECE没关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE不是后天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥!?  你不是自己说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你装什么装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那里已经全黑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.41,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}注：据说女性[哔——]多了某处就会变黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦! 别碰我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你个…头!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我放手!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?  安城?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在和宿海他们玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家 这边!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么啊 耍这种花招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救被男人缠上的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是我一生中所做的最普通的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救 就那样?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该揍他一顿再拉我走么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我头脑好 长得又帅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜没腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是 很傻很天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想被你这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个女装男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 还是被骂来得舒坦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是处女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有 有有有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我交往试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你 你你喜欢芽间的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那个样子哪里好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便配对啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有说喜欢什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的领队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑好 运动好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是以前的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有时候会很体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发好好整理一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.26,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Hey! Say! JUMP：男性偶像团体，「小山」指山田涼介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有点儿像Hey! Say! JUMP的小山…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 到底是不是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是 在意宿海而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也变得好像很难说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进了同一所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实本来还有些高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海忘不了芽间的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海忘不了芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘不了宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才雪集你 用了宿海的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.14,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}特快列车经过 请稍侯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 掉队了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚咚咚 叮!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:08.24,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}注：这句话为搞笑艺人原西孝幸名段子的首句 \N也是为死者上香时所敲木鱼和小钟的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在我家吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是带山菜了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是天麸罗好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波 看上去吃得很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子上面脏了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 芽间在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 在的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也来吃吧 天麸罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我后来又仔细想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大概芽间在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会留在这里吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成…佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种 那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 芽间在那里么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给一点点提示 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会为你「咚咚咚叮」的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 也依靠一下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你成佛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 久川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我吧 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不要只在仁碳面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在我的面前现个身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗? 喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}听我说 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.44,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}和大家一起来 好好地想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成佛什么的 这些东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:13.96,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:14.89,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}大家一起考虑吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 芽间也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------ED-------------------
